  "description": "Daisy/composite/aster family — ~1,911 genera, ~32,000+ species (largest angiosperm family). Diagnostic composite flower head (capitulum) composed of ray and disc florets, inferior ovary, pappus for wind dispersal. Includes sunflower, lettuce, chamomile, dandelion, artichoke.",
